{"tid":906884,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"巴打門有冇拉得嘅背囊介紹","createTime":"2018-11-18T10:57:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-18T11:25:00.000Z","uid":193601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"11604ebc5c3754724e83fc6644a6cd8a2ac1751a","tid":906884,"uid":193601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T10:57:45.000Z","msg":"男朋友就嚟生日<br />\n佢返工有好多嘢拎<br />\n佢之前講過想拉車仔返工<br />\n我見好多電訊公司嘅人都係拉喼<br />\n但佢又唔想要個行李喼<br />\n所以想搵個靚靚哋拉得嘅背囊<br />\n唔知其實叫咩名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以上網搵得好少<br />\n有冇巴打有啲靚嘅介紹<br />\n我淨係搵到幾款 但好似麻麻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yEzLina.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyEzLina.png&h=7b85e56f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8rTW9tQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8rTW9tQ.png&h=a4d94e2c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xU4Z7fw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxU4Z7fw.png&h=6b4de4ea&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"87bcef7bb84f537174ed0e546dd3e7971fb8b89b","tid":906884,"uid":193601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T10:59:02.000Z","msg":"同埋其實依啲好唔好碌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好驚好難控制 好難拉 拉得唔順<br />\n上網買又冇得試<br />\n但又唔知香港有冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03c8478974af39bce530f70821dd5f57bbff42ce","tid":906884,"uid":5181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T11:03:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://goo.gl/images/fYpzn7\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fimages%2FfYpzn7&h=30db749b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"75fdc59cfde4f6549a366bbc56de0e5bc70069bb","tid":906884,"uid":193601,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T11:03:50.000Z","msg":"巴打*們<img src=\"/assets/faces/n